snippet.title: STRINOVA GLOBAL LAUNCH SEASON 1 - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
The future of humanity — will it sustain the stability of the new world, rebuild their shattered homes, or pursue endless possibilities? Stringification empowers our abilities, and brings out our desires...

Welcome to STRINOVA! A free-to-play 5v5 Anime-Style Shooter game. The game is available on both PC and Steam from Nov 21st, 2024 onwards.
Website: https://strinova.link/RhI5T
Steam: https://strinova.link/1p3gVv

Stay tuned for gameplay clips, patch updates and a whole lot more on our social media platforms below:
Twitter：https://x.com/Strinova_EN
Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/Strinova
Discord：https://discord.gg/strinova
